  "title": "Hydraulic Technician (Valves & Pumps) #79393",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacture and Repair of Pumps</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Hydraulic Service Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pioneer</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday-Friday, 8AM – 5PM; Saturday, 8AM-12PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Meal Allowance + OT + AWS + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform assembly, installation, and maintenance of hydraulic components and systems.</li><li>Participate in pressure testing of hydraulic components.</li><li>Assist engineers in troubleshooting and diagnosing issues in existing hydraulic systems.</li><li>Prepare accurate testing reports, service reports, and maintenance records for completed projects.</li><li>Carry out mechanical repair work for hydraulic equipment and components in both workshop and shipyard environments.</li><li>Work under supervision of senior technicians and engineers initially, progressing to independent work once competency is demonstrated.</li><li>Coordinate deliveries with relevant stakeholders.</li><li>Arrange entry permits for work at shipyards.</li><li>Act as liaison between the technical department and the admin department.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Possession of a valid driving license is preferred.</li><li>Strong willingness to learn and adapt.</li><li>Training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79393 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
